# GEOGRAPHY AREAS 2.0 – GLOBAL MARKET ACCESS & DEPLOYMENT CONTROL CENTER

## Objective

Transform this screen from a static configuration page into a strategic geographic intelligence center.

The goal is not simply to define countries.

The goal is to manage:

- Market availability
- Regulatory approval status
- Product visibility
- Pricing regions
- Distributor territories
- Clinic access
- Shipping restrictions
- Supplier sourcing regions
- Revenue by geography
- Zoho customer segmentation
- International expansion planning

The experience must be fully responsive and operational on both desktop and mobile.

